<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Password Changed</title>
    <style>
        body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; }
        .header { background: #27ae60; color: white; padding: 30px; text-align: center; border-radius: 8px 8px 0 0; }
        .content { background: #f9f9f9; padding: 30px; border-radius: 0 0 8px 8px; }
        .success-box { background: #d4edda; border-left: 4px solid #27ae60; padding: 20px; margin: 20px 0; border-radius: 0 5px 5px 0; }
        .button { display: inline-block; background: #e74c3c; color: white; padding: 12px 30px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 5px; margin: 20px 0; }
        .footer { text-align: center; margin-top: 30px; color: #666; font-size: 12px; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="header">
        <h1>✅ Password Changed</h1>
        <p>Your account is secure</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="content">
        <h2>Hello {{firstName}} {{lastName}},</h2>
        
        <div class="success-box">
            <strong>✅ Success:</strong> Your {{appName}} account password has been changed successfully.
        </div>
        
        <p>This email confirms that your password was recently updated. Your account is now more secure with your new password.</p>
        
        <h3>Security Tips:</h3>
        <ul>
            <li>Use a unique password that you don't use elsewhere</li>
            <li>Consider enabling two-factor authentication</li>
            <li>Keep your password private and secure</li>
            <li>Regularly review your account activity</li>
        </ul>
        
        <p><strong>If you didn't change your password:</strong></p>
        <p>Someone else may have access to your account. Take these steps immediately:</p>
        <ol>
            <li>Change your password again</li>
            <li>Review your account activity</li>
            <li>Contact our support team</li>
            <li>Enable two-factor authentication</li>
        </ol>
        
        <a href="{{appUrl}}/account/security" class="button">Review Account Security</a>
        
        <p>Best regards,<br>The {{appName}} Team</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="footer">
        <p>{{appName}} | <a href="{{appUrl}}">{{appUrl}}</a></p>
        <p>This is an automated security notification.</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>